{"tid":1802813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持港獨手足入黎駁下我","createTime":"2019-12-29T17:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T15:31:05.000Z","uid":207390,"like":31,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f8e997c8d5946d26ca344b6faf275fb18bdeec","tid":1802813,"uid":207390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:49:44.000Z","msg":"我深信連登係一個同溫層<br />\n連登絕大部分人係運動前/運動後都同意港獨係有需要<br />\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\<br />\n事實係未係時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不服來辯<br />\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>個人認為現階段唔應該以港獨為主線，因為可行性不足:<br />\n1）軍權<br />\n2）政權<br />\n3）人民獨立意願<br />\n4）人民革命意願</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個係雨傘時期已經討論過.....<br />\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\<br />\n爭取真普選(五大訴求)，先會引發更多可能性出現<br />\n再講獨立<br />\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\<br />\nQ&amp;A:<br />\n1.係中共眼中，真普選等同獨立，所以唔可能存在真普選。<br />\n--&gt;係條文上，中共應該給予香港真普選。呢個係其他國家可以藉此同中共傾數嘅理由。<br />\n所以我地應該保持返團火，同時繼續文宣輸出，要形成冷戰包圍網。<br />\n<br />\n2.現階段叫唔叫香港獨立好?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">--&gt;兄弟爬山，互相支持就可以，不割蓆</span></strong>"},{"pid":"aad9722e761ff8e3f503424a22b9ad5401f8187a","tid":1802813,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:56:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d267bdccaf9e696955d88b97f51d503a7db1e68","tid":1802813,"uid":288670,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:56:41.000Z","msg":"依家個發展真係好撚似撐加泰集會 又有一班連登狗俾五毛帶風向 屌手足係鬼 又有一班鬼拎所羅門出黎屌手足"},{"pid":"74e048506c44281f46e957853101e310c8483aa9","tid":1802813,"uid":95520,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:57:42.000Z","msg":"就係因為3同4<br />\n所以先應該而家開始講<br />\n做好教育工作<br />\n<br />\n港獨不可騎劫運動,但而家一定會係最佳嘅教育時機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525193</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79b5e69133230b22c16be6f3f3952583beff87b3","tid":1802813,"uid":30836,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:58:09.000Z","msg":"連登呢個同溫層以外大把人嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ff876e845be0f7879a27710aa480a002c7764b","tid":1802813,"uid":235769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"前線退，和你shop，集會都有手足嗌香港獨立 連登仔：獨立係風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802815</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29295d816ba9d6a0f6ce796edd5536be5d5e0d37","tid":1802813,"uid":272952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"74e048506c44281f46e957853101e310c8483aa9","tid":1802813,"uid":95520,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:57:42.000Z","msg":"就係因為3同4<br />\n所以先應該而家開始講<br />\n做好教育工作<br />\n<br />\n港獨不可騎劫運動,但而家一定會係最佳嘅教育時機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525193</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T18:02:14.000Z","msg":"同意，依家就係要種下一粒種子，等待發芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似光復香港，時代革命咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年天琦講嗰陣都唔係個個BUY<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但721打後己經遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6